OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWaitrose changes Christmas 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fadvert after complaints    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Waitrose has changed a part of its     
OL,6, Christmas advert that showed two       
OL,7, farmers comparing sun tans after it was
OL,8, criticised by skin cancer patients.    
OL,10,FThe supermarket apologised last week   
OL,11,Fafter it received a backlash to its    
OL,12,Fvideo on social media.                 
OL,14,FCritics said a section of the advert   
OL,15,Fglorified sun tans and failed to       
OL,16,Fhighlight the dangers of sunlight.     
OL,18,FWaitrose told the BBC it would now be  
OL,19,Fusing an "updated version of the ad to 
OL,20,Faddress these concerns".               
